In environment X : Type Y : Type eqX : eq_dec X eqY : eq_dec Y x, y : X * Y Unable to unify "y" with "x".
Not an inductive goal with 2 constructors.

original: intros eqX eqY. intros x y. destruct eqX as [eqX_true | eqX_false], eqY as [eqY_true | eqY_false]. - left. split; auto. - right. intro H. destruct H as [H1 H2]. apply eqX_false. auto. - right. intro H. destruct H as [H1 H2]. apply eqY_false. auto. - right. intro H. destruct H as [H1 H2]. apply eqX_false. auto.
